📘 Task 1: Data Preprocessing Pipeline

📄 Description

This task demonstrates a complete ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) pipeline using Pandas and Scikit-learn.

📁 Files

data_preprocessing_pipeline.ipynb – Contains all preprocessing steps

X_train.csv, X_test.csv, y_train.csv, y_test.csv – Processed datasets

🧪 Steps Performed

Loaded Titanic dataset

Handled missing values (Age, Embarked)

Dropped irrelevant column (Cabin)

Encoded categorical variables (Sex, Embarked)

Scaled numerical features (Age, Fare, Pclass)

Split into train-test sets

🛠️ Libraries Used

pandas

numpy

scikit-learn

✅ Output

Cleaned, encoded, and scaled data saved to CSV files for modeling.

